  "title": "Tapping for money shame",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for the guilt and regret around past financial decisions.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 5 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the shame loop around past money mistakes: the replayed decisions, the regret, the fear that those choices have closed off what's possible now. Use when the old guilt is loud, not when you're making a new decision.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 5 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Release shame about past mistakes.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
